# Secrets / env
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
credentials*
secrets*
# …but memory/credentials.py is the credential-VOCABULARY seam — a source module
# with no secrets in it. The patterns above are for secret files; keep it tracked.
!src/salient_core/memory/credentials.py

